  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Innovative development planning integrating adaptation to climate change in Mali</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project built competencies for climate change adaptation among national and local decision-makers. This enabled them to identify appropriate, effective measures, integrate them into decentralised development planning, and carry them out. To achieve this, the project offered basic and further training in the field of climate change and adaptation, and established a platform for sharing experience. The project partners helped the regional authorities to implement concrete adaptation measures and presented the outcomes and experiences of the project at national, international and regional forums and conferences. In addition, they lobbied to raise awareness on the need for adaptation measures, identifyied financing mechanisms at a decentralised level and developed innovative methods and tools for integrating adaptation measures into decentralised development strategies.</narrative>
  </description>
